<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="N%20Engl%20J%20Med"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Observational Study of Hydroxychloroquine in Hospitalized Patients with Covid-19</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Geleris%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Joshua Geleris</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Joshua Geleris</span>, <span class="degrees">M.D.</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>From the Divisions of General Medicine, Infectious Diseases, and Pulmonary, Allergy, and Critical Care Medicine, Department of Medicine (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K., R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.), the Departments of Biostatistics (Y.S.) and Epidemiology (J.P., R.G.B., N.W.S.), Mailman School of Public Health, and the Department of Biomedical Informatics (G.H.), Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, and New York–Presbyterian Hospital–Columbia University Irving Medical Center (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K.,R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.) — all in New York.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Geleris%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Joshua Geleris</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sun%20Y"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Yifei Sun</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Yifei Sun</span>, <span class="degrees">Ph.D.</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>From the Divisions of General Medicine, Infectious Diseases, and Pulmonary, Allergy, and Critical Care Medicine, Department of Medicine (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K., R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.), the Departments of Biostatistics (Y.S.) and Epidemiology (J.P., R.G.B., N.W.S.), Mailman School of Public Health, and the Department of Biomedical Informatics (G.H.), Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, and New York–Presbyterian Hospital–Columbia University Irving Medical Center (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K.,R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.) — all in New York.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sun%20Y"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Yifei Sun</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Platt%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Jonathan Platt</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Jonathan Platt</span>, <span class="degrees">Ph.D.</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>From the Divisions of General Medicine, Infectious Diseases, and Pulmonary, Allergy, and Critical Care Medicine, Department of Medicine (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K., R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.), the Departments of Biostatistics (Y.S.) and Epidemiology (J.P., R.G.B., N.W.S.), Mailman School of Public Health, and the Department of Biomedical Informatics (G.H.), Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, and New York–Presbyterian Hospital–Columbia University Irving Medical Center (J.G., J.Z., M.B., A.L., D.K.M., C.K.,R.G.B., M.E.S., N.W.S.) — all in New York.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Platt%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Jonathan Platt</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Zucker%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Jason Zucker</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Jason Zucker</span>, <span class="degrees">M.D.</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
